scene_description: The grid of pixels is split into another grid of pixels using a single color. Some cells of the new grid are filled in with colors (other than black).
literal_instruction: The grid of pixels is split into another grid of pixels using a single color. Some cells of the new grid are filled in with colors (other than black). Cells of like colors must be connected, using only straight lines and right angles. To draw a line, fill in the cell next to a colored cell with the same color, and repeat this process until two of the original like colored cells are connected.
